### ===========================================
### LOGIN REQUESTS
### ===========================================
### Use VS Code REST Client extension to run these requests
### Install: ms-vscode.rest-client
### ===========================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

### -----------------------------------------
### Login as Alice (successful)
### -----------------------------------------
### Copy the token from the response to use in other requests

# @name loginAlice
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "SecurePass123!"
}

### -----------------------------------------
### Login as Bob (successful)
### -----------------------------------------

# @name loginBob
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "bob",
  "password": "BobSecure2026!"
}

### -----------------------------------------
### Login with invalid password (should fail - 401)
### -----------------------------------------

POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "WrongPassword123"
}

